    "body": "Hey @cruzdanilo, thanks for opening this issue. We should update this plugin to 3.x.\r\n\r\nSetting a dependency as peer doesn't mean that you can choose a different major version than what's been specified. The semantics of peerDependencies is different, and they are now installed automatically by npm7.\r\n\r\nWe will update the plugin to 3.x asap.",
